title: Kore wa Kitto Yume no Naka no Kiss
original_name: これはきっと夢の中のキス
sinopse:
Minato has a habit of dating guys who are pretty abusive, and the one he's seeing now is no exemption. One day, he notices a certain customer who keeps gazing on a sculptor outside the cafe. It turns out that he is the very artist responsible for that creation.

(Source: MU)

Included one-shot: Misshitsu Renai
